 more regular rhythmic bursts in the {MS} and sharper {MS}{HIPP} {GC} spectra without a significant increase in {MS}{HIPP} {GC} magnitude. The results of this study suggest an essential role of descending {HIPP} to {MS} projections in theta generation.},
