ne-treated controls or kainate-injected rats 2–4 days after treatment. In conclusion, the prolonged negative field-potential shifts evoked to perforant path stimulation in normal {ACSF} were associated with mossy fiber reorganization, but the relative contribution of altered inhibition, increased synaptic excitation, or even non-synaptic mechanisms is unknown.},
